cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.DS 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and taxonomy extraction from text. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses embeddings and machine learning techniques to improve taxonomy induction. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with intelligent systems that can automatically refine taxonomies. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with extracting taxonomies from text, which is a common task in information retrieval. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is another possible category as the paper proposes a new algorithm for taxonomy refinement based on hyperbolic term embeddings.
